StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetMapSectorsHavingZipCodes]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@Recrui.ngOrgID uniqueidentifier AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT DISTINCT(SectorDesignator), ms.SectorID, ms.Recrui.ngOrganiza.onId, ms.LastUpdateUserId FROM usmc.MapsSector ms INNER JOIN usmc.MapsSectorZip msz ON msz.SectorID = ms.SectorID WHERE ms.Recrui.ngOrganiza.onId = @Recrui.ngOrgID ORDER BY ms.SectorDesignator
END
